{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775897370846,"sessionID":"ses_28444dcffffeVsazahFTZhj6mv","part":{"id":"prt_d7bbb5bd7001CpgzlQNKcGhoBB","messageID":"msg_d7bbb3db5001xO4Foc1GbRCaEH","sessionID":"ses_28444dcffffeVsazahFTZhj6mv","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_617838c8d8d4411189089a95","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-038/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-038/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/workloadmanager\n4: **Language:** Go\n5: **Size:** L\n6: \n7: ## Purpose\n8: \n9: 为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块补齐缺失的 Go 单元测试，覆盖 reconciler 核心协调逻辑、handler sandbox 创建流程、及顶层常量定义。已有测试（response、lifecycle、delete、metrics）保持不变。目标是提升关键路径代码覆盖率、防止回归、为后续重构提供安全网。\n10: \n11: ## Scope\n12: \n13: ### In Scope\n14: \n15: 1. **reconciler/reconciler_test.go** — `SandboxReconciler` 生命周期测试\n16:    - `NewSandboxReconciler` 参数校验（nil Store/Clientset/InformerFactory panic）\n17:    - `Run` 幂等性（重复调用忽略）、cache sync 成功/失败路径\n18:    - `Enqueue` key 格式（带/不带 namespace）、metrics 触发\n19:    - `WatchSandboxOnce` 正常返回、超时返回\n20: \n21: 2. **reconciler/sync_test.go** — 工作队列与 sync 流程测试\n22:    - `syncHandler` key 解析（有效/无效格式）\n23:    - AgentRuntime 存在 → `reconcileAgentRuntime`\n24:    - CodeInterpreter 存在 → `reconcileCodeInterpreter`\n25:    - Pod 存在 → `reconcilePod`\n26:    - 三者均不存在 → 返回 nil\n27:    - `processNextWorkItem` 重试逻辑（maxRetries=15、指数退避、超时强制退出）\n28:    - `determineResourceType` 根据 lister 结果推断资源类型\n29: \n30: 3. **reconciler/agentruntime_test.go** — AgentRuntime 协调测试\n31:    - `mapConditionToStatus` 条件映射（Ready=True→running、Ready=False+Terminated→terminated、Ready=False→pending、Ready=Unknown→pending、无条件→pending）\n32:    - `reconcileAgentRuntime` 正常路径：lister 获取 → session-id 标签 → Store 不存在则 StoreSandbox、存在且状态变化则 UpdateSandbox\n33:    - DeletionTimestamp 非空 → DeleteSandboxBySessionID\n34:    - session-id 标签缺失 → 跳过\n35:    - Store 操作失败 → 返回错误 + metrics 记录\n36: \n37: 4. **reconciler/codeinterpreter_test.go** — CodeInterpreter 协调测试\n38:    - 与 AgentRuntime 对称的测试场景\n39:    - WarmPoolSize > 0 日志路径验证\n40:    - Kind 字段为 \"CodeInterpreter\"\n41: \n42: 5. **reconciler/pod_test.go** — Pod 协调测试\n43:    - `reconcilePod` 正常路径：sandbox-name 标签 → Pod Running + IP 非空 → ListSandboxes 匹配 → UpdateSandbox PodIP\n44:    - sandbox-name 标签缺失 → 跳过\n45:    - Pod 非 Running 或 IP 为空 → 跳过\n46:    - PodIP 未变化 → 跳过\n47:    - `buildEntryPointsFromSandboxInfo` 端点 IP 替换\n48:    - `extractPort` 端口提取（含/不含冒号）\n49: \n50: 6. **reconciler/event_handlers_test.go** — 事件处理器测试\n51:    - AgentRuntime Add/Update/Delete → workqueue.Add + metrics\n52:    - CodeInterpreter Add/Update/Delete → workqueue.Add + metrics\n53:    - Pod Add → sandbox-name 标签检查 → workqueue.Add\n54:    - Pod Update → oldRunning→newRunning 或 ipChanged 才入队\n55:    - Pod Delete → 仅日志，不入队\n56:    - `cache.DeletedFinalStateUnknown` tombstone 处理\n57: \n58: 7. **handler/sandbox_create_test.go** — Sandbox 创建 handler 测试\n59:    - `CreateSandboxRequest.Validate` 校验（kind/namespace/name 必填、kind 枚举值）\n60:    - `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 请求解析 → template 查找 → sessionID/sandboxName 生成 → CR 构建 → StoreSandbox → WatchSandboxOnce → dynamicClient.Create → PodIP 解析 → UpdateSandbox → 响应\n61:    - `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox` 同上 + WarmPoolSize > 0 → SandboxClaim 路径\n62:    - `injectPicodAuthEnv` AuthModePicoD 注入\n63:    - `rollbackCR` 回滚逻辑（正常删除、AlreadyNotFound）\n64:    - `buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR` CR 构建（labels、annotations、spec、podTemplate 转换）\n65:    - `buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR` CR 构建（warm pool 分支、Sandbox vs SandboxClaim）\n66:    - `resolvePodIP` 多种解析策略（直接 Get、Annotation、LabelSelector + OwnerReference）\n67:    - `buildEntryPoints` 端点构建\n68:    - `generateSessionID` / `generateSandboxName` / `RandString`\n69:    - `getDynamicClient` auth 开启/关闭、token cache、user client factory\n70: \n71: 8. **const.go** — 顶层常量验证\n72:    - `LastActivityAnnotationKey` 值验证\n73: \n74: ### Out of Scope\n75: \n76: - 集成测试（需要真实 Kubernetes API server）\n77: - E2E 测试（需要完整 AgentCube 平台环境）\n78: - 性能/基准测试（后续单独 AR）\n79: - 修改 workloadmanager 生产代码（仅新增 `*_test.go` 文件）\n80: - 已有测试文件的修改（response_test.go、sandbox_lifecycle_test.go、sandbox_delete_test.go、metrics_test.go）\n81: \n82: ## Architecture Summary\n83: \n84: ### Current State\n85: \n86: `pkg/workloadmanager/` 模块结构：\n87: \n88: ```\n89: pkg/workloadmanager/\n90: ├── const.go                          # 顶层常量\n91: ├── handler/\n92: │   ├── constants.go                  # GVR、Kind、Label、Annotation 常量\n93: │   ├── models.go                     # 数据模型 + MetricsRecorder 接口\n94: │   ├── sandbox_create.go             # Sandbox 创建 handler（AgentRuntime + CodeInterpreter）\n95: │   ├── sandbox_delete.go             # Sandbox 删除 handler\n96: │   ├── sandbox_lifecycle.go          # 生命周期管理（GC、TTL、idle、status、list、extend）\n97: │   ├── sandbox_lifecycle_test.go     # ✅ 已有测试\n98: │   └── sandbox_delete_test.go        # ✅ 已有测试\n99: ├── reconciler/\n100: │   ├── reconciler.go                 # SandboxReconciler 主控制器\n101: │   ├── sync.go                       # syncHandler + workqueue 处理\n102: │   ├── agentruntime.go               # AgentRuntime 协调逻辑\n103: │   ├── codeinterpreter.go            # CodeInterpreter 协调逻辑\n104: │   ├── pod.go                        # Pod 协调逻辑\n105: │   ├── event_handlers.go             # Informer 事件处理\n106: │   ├── types.go                      # Store 接口 + ReconcilerDeps\n107: │   ├── metrics.go                    # PrometheusMetricsRecorder\n108: │   └── metrics_test.go               # ✅ 已有测试\n109: └── response/\n110:     ├── response.go                   # HTTP 响应工具\n111:     └── response_test.go              # ✅ 已有测试\n112: ```\n113: \n114: **已有测试覆盖**：\n115: - `response/` — JSON/Error/Created/ErrorWithID 全部覆盖\n116: - `handler/sandbox_lifecycle_test.go` — LifecycleManager 构造、过期判断、Start/Stop、GetSandboxStatus、ListSandboxes、ExtendSandboxTTL、GC 清理、边界条件\n117: - `handler/sandbox_delete_test.go` — DeleteSandboxRequest 校验、resolveGVR、MockStore 全操作\n118: - `reconciler/metrics_test.go` — PrometheusMetricsRecorder 全部方法 + nil receiver 安全\n119: \n120: **测试缺口**：\n121: - `reconciler/` — 核心协调逻辑（reconciler.go、sync.go、agentruntime.go、codeinterpreter.go、pod.go、event_handlers.go）完全无测试\n122: - `handler/sandbox_create.go` — 创建流程完全无测试\n123: - `const.go` — 顶层常量无验证\n124: \n125: ### Target State\n126: \n127: 新增以下测试文件，与现有测试风格一致（testify + table-driven + mock）：\n128: \n129: | 文件 | 覆盖目标 |\n130: |------|----------|\n131: | `reconciler/reconciler_test.go` | NewSandboxReconciler、Run、Enqueue、WatchSandboxOnce |\n132: | `reconciler/sync_test.go` | syncHandler、processNextWorkItem、determineResourceType |\n133: | `reconciler/agentruntime_test.go` | mapConditionToStatus、reconcileAgentRuntime |\n134: | `reconciler/codeinterpreter_test.go` | reconcileCodeInterpreter |\n135: | `reconciler/pod_test.go` | reconcilePod、buildEntryPointsFromSandboxInfo、extractPort |\n136: | `reconciler/event_handlers_test.go` | 9 个事件处理函数 |\n137: | `handler/sandbox_create_test.go` | 创建流程全路径 |\n138: | `const_test.go` | 顶层常量验证 |\n139: \n140: ## Impact Analysis\n141: \n142: ### Dependencies\n143: \n144: | 依赖 | 来源 | 说明 |\n145: |------|------|------|\n146: | `testing` | Go stdlib | 标准测试框架 |\n147: | `github.com/stretchr/testify` | go.mod | 断言库（项目已使用） |\n148: | `net/http/httptest` | Go stdlib | HTTP handler 测试 |\n149: | `k8s.io/client-go/dynamic/fake` | go.mod | fake dynamic client |\n150: | `k8s.io/client-go/testing` | go.mod | reactor 机制 |\n151: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime` | go.mod | scheme 注册 |\n152: \n153: ### Affected Components\n154: \n155: | 文件/目录 | 状态 | 说明 |\n156: |-----------|------|------|\n157: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/reconciler_test.go` | 新增 | Reconciler 生命周期测试 |\n158: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/sync_test.go` | 新增 | Sync 流程测试 |\n159: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/agentruntime_test.go` | 新增 | AgentRuntime 协调测试 |\n160: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/codeinterpreter_test.go` | 新增 | CodeInterpreter 协调测试 |\n161: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/pod_test.go` | 新增 | Pod 协调测试 |\n162: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/event_handlers_test.go` | 新增 | 事件处理测试 |\n163: | `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_create_test.go` | 新增 | 创建 handler 测试 |\n164: | `pkg/workloadmanager/const_test.go` | 新增 | 顶层常量验证 |\n165: | `pkg/workloadmanager/` | 无变更 | 生产代码不修改 |\n166: \n167: ### Risk Assessment\n168: \n169: | 风险 | 等级 | 缓解措施 |\n170: |------|------|----------|\n171: | `SandboxReconciler.Run` 阻塞式调用难以在单测中验证 | 高 | 使用 goroutine + channel 传递结果，设置超时 |\n172: | Informer factory 需要真实 client 或复杂 mock | 高 | 使用 `fake.NewSimpleDynamicClient` + 手动触发 informer 事件 |\n173: | `WatchSandboxOnce` 依赖 lister 异步填充 | 中 | 使用 channel 控制 lister 返回时机 |\n174: | `processNextWorkItem` 重试逻辑涉及时间（指数退避） | 中 | mock workqueue 或使用 `FakeRateLimitingQueue` |\n175: | sandbox_create 涉及 dynamic client + kube clientset 双重依赖 | 中 | 分别 mock，使用 fake clientset + fake dynamic client |\n176: | 测试数据构造复杂（CR 结构、pod spec 转换） | 低 | 复用现有 `buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR` 逻辑验证输出结构 |\n177: \n178: ## Alternatives Considered\n179: \n180: ### 1. Table-driven tests vs. individual test functions（✅ 选定 table-driven）\n181: \n182: - **Table-driven**：Go 惯用法，易于扩展，减少样板代码，与现有测试风格一致\n183: - **Individual functions**：每个场景独立函数，更清晰但冗余\n184: - **决策**：以 table-driven 为主（`mapConditionToStatus`、`extractPort`、事件处理等），复杂异步场景辅以独立函数（`Run`、`WatchSandboxOnce`）\n185: \n186: ### 2. testify vs. 标准库（✅ 选定 testify）\n187: \n188: - **testify**：项目已使用 `github.com/stretchr/testify/assert` 和 `require`，保持一致\n189: - **标准库**：零依赖，但断言需手动实现\n190: - **决策**：跟随项目现有测试风格\n191: \n192: ### 3. Mock interface vs. fake clientset（✅ 选定混合策略）\n193: \n194: - **Mock interface**：对 `Store`、`MetricsRecorder` 使用手写 mock（已有 `mockStore` 模式）\n195: - **Fake clientset**：对 Kubernetes 客户端使用 `k8s.io/client-go` 内置 fake 实现\n196: - **决策**：Store/MetricsRecorder 用手写 mock（简单可控），Kubernetes 客户端用 fake（行为真实）\n197: \n198: ### 4. 测试完整 Run 循环 vs. 拆分测试（✅ 选定拆分测试）\n199: \n200: - **完整 Run 循环**：启动真实 informer + workqueue + workers，验证端到端\n201: - **拆分测试**：分别测试 NewSandboxReconciler、Enqueue、syncHandler、processNextWorkItem\n202: - **决策**：拆分测试。Run 循环涉及 goroutine 和阻塞调用，单测中难以可靠验证。通过测试各组件间接保证 Run 正确性。`WatchSandboxOnce` 作为唯一的异步公开方法单独测试。\n203: \n204: ## Upstream Dependencies\n205: \n206: - `pkg/workloadmanager/` 生产代码稳定\n207: - `client-go/` 生成的 Kubernetes 客户端代码可用（fake clientset、informers、listers）\n208: - Go 测试工具链可用（`go test`）\n209: \n210: ## Test Strategy\n211: \n212: ### Mock Objects\n213: \n214: | Mock | 用途 | 实现方式 |\n215: |------|------|----------|\n216: | `mockStore` | Store 接口模拟 | 已有（sandbox_delete_test.go 中的 `mockStore`，提取为共享 fixture） |\n217: | `mockMetricsRecorder` | MetricsRecorder 接口模拟 | 新建，记录调用次数和参数 |\n218: | `fake dynamic.Client` | Kubernetes 动态客户端 | `k8s.io/client-go/dynamic/fake` |\n219: | `fake clientset.Clientset` | 类型化客户端 | `client-go/clientset/versioned/fake` |\n220: | `fake informer factory` | Informer 工厂 | 手动构造 + 手动 Add 对象 |\n221: \n222: ### Test Categories\n223: \n224: 1. **Unit tests**（纯函数）：`mapConditionToStatus`、`extractPort`、`Validate`、`RandString`\n225: 2. **Mock-based tests**（依赖注入）：`reconcileAgentRuntime`、`reconcileCodeInterpreter`、`reconcilePod`、事件处理\n226: 3. **HTTP handler tests**（httptest）：`CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox`、`CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox`\n227: 4. **Async tests**（goroutine + channel）：`WatchSandboxOnce`\n228: \n229: ## Acceptance Criteria\n230: \n231: 1. **reconciler/**\n232:    - [ ] `NewSandboxReconciler` nil 参数 panic 测试（Store、Clientset、InformerFactory）\n233:    - [ ] `NewSandboxReconciler` 默认 workers=2 验证\n234:    - [ ] `Enqueue` 带/不带 namespace 的 key 格式验证\n235:    - [ ] `Enqueue` metricsRecorder 非空时触发 IncWorkqueueAdds\n236:    - [ ] `Run` 幂等性（重复调用返回）\n237:    - [ ] `WatchSandboxOnce` AgentRuntime 存在且 Ready → 返回 running\n238:    - [ ] `WatchSandboxOnce` 超时 → 返回 error\n239:    - [ ] `syncHandler` 无效 key → 返回错误\n240:    - [ ] `syncHandler` AgentRuntime 存在 → reconcileAgentRuntime\n241:    - [ ] `syncHandler` CodeInterpreter 存在 → reconcileCodeInterpreter\n242:    - [ ] `syncHandler` Pod 存在 → reconcilePod\n243:    - [ ] `syncHandler` 三者均不存在 → nil\n244:    - [ ] `processNextWorkItem` 错误重试（< maxRetries 入队、>= maxRetries Forget）\n245:    - [ ] `mapConditionToStatus` 全部条件分支覆盖（5 个 case）\n246:    - [ ] `reconcileAgentRuntime` 新资源 → StoreSandbox\n247:    - [ ] `reconcileAgentRuntime` 状态变化 → UpdateSandbox\n248:    - [ ] `reconcileAgentRuntime` terminated → DeleteSandboxBySessionID\n249:    - [ ] `reconcileAgentRuntime` DeletionTimestamp → DeleteSandboxBySessionID\n250:    - [ ] `reconcileAgentRuntime` session-id 缺失 → 跳过\n251:    - [ ] `reconcileCodeInterpreter` 与 AgentRuntime 对称场景\n252:    - [ ] `reconcileCodeInterpreter` WarmPoolSize > 0 日志路径\n253:    - [ ] `reconcilePod` Running + IP 变化 → UpdateSandbox\n254:    - [ ] `reconcilePod` 非 Running / 无 IP / 无 sandbox-name → 跳过\n255:    - [ ] `buildEntryPointsFromSandboxInfo` 端点 IP 替换\n256:    - [ ] `extractPort` 端口提取（含冒号、不含冒号）\n257:    - [ ] 全部 9 个事件处理函数入队验证\n258:    - [ ] Pod Update 条件过滤（oldRunning→newRunning 或 ipChanged）\n259:    - [ ] Pod Delete 仅日志不入队\n260:    - [ ] tombstone（DeletedFinalStateUnknown）处理\n261: \n262: 2. **handler/sandbox_create_test.go**\n263:    - [ ] `CreateSandboxRequest.Validate` 全部校验分支\n264:    - [ ] `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 成功路径\n265:    - [ ] `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 请求体无效 → 400\n266:    - [ ] `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` template 不存在 → 404\n267:    - [ ] `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` podTemplate 缺失 → 400\n268:    - [ ] `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` Watch 超时 → 回滚 + 500\n269:    - [ ] `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox` 成功路径\n270:    - [ ] `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox` WarmPoolSize > 0 → SandboxClaim\n271:    - [ ] `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox` AuthModePicoD → injectPicodAuthEnv\n272:    - [ ] `buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR` 输出结构验证（labels、annotations、spec）\n273:    - [ ] `buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR` warm pool 分支 → SandboxClaim\n274:    - [ ] `buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR` 非 warm pool → Sandbox\n275:    - [ ] `resolvePodIP` 直接 Get 成功\n276:    - [ ] `resolvePodIP` Annotation 回退\n277:    - [ ] `resolvePodIP` LabelSelector + OwnerReference 回退\n278:    - [ ] `resolvePodIP` 全部失败 → 错误\n279:    - [ ] `rollbackCR` 正常删除\n280:    - [ ] `rollbackCR` AlreadyNotFound → 忽略\n281:    - [ ] `getDynamicClient` auth 关闭 → 返回默认 client\n282:    - [ ] `getDynamicClient` auth 开启 + token cache → 调用 cache\n283:    - [ ] `getDynamicClient` auth 开启 + 无 token → 错误\n284:    - [ ] `buildEntryPoints` 多端口端点构建\n285:    - [ ] `RandString` 长度和字符集验证\n286: \n287: 3. **const.go**\n288:    - [ ] `LastActivityAnnotationKey` == \"last-activity-time\"\n289: \n290: ## Status\n291: \n292: - [ ] Proposal review\n293: - [ ] Implementation\n294: - [ ] Verification\n\n(End of file - total 294 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n\n**Module:** pkg/workloadmanager\n**Language:** Go\n**Size:** L\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块补齐缺失的 Go 单元测试，覆盖 reconciler 核心协调逻辑、handler sandbox 创建流程、及顶层常量定义。已有测试（response、lifecycle、delete、metrics）保持不变。目标是提升关键路径代码覆盖率、防止回归、为后续重构提供安全网。\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n1. **reconciler/reconciler_test.go** — `SandboxReconciler` 生命周期测试\n   - `NewSandboxReconciler` 参数校验（nil Store/Clientset/InformerFactory panic）\n   - `Run` 幂等性（重复调用忽略）、cache sync 成功/失败路径\n   - `Enqueue` key 格式（带/不带 namespace）、metrics 触发\n   - `WatchSandboxOnce` 正常返回、超时返回\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-038/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775897370823,"end":1775897370844}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775897372317,"sessionID":"ses_28444dcffffeVsazahFTZhj6mv","part":{"id":"prt_d7bbb6179001phBIkVXDz3FAcT","messageID":"msg_d7bbb3db5001xO4Foc1GbRCaEH","sessionID":"ses_28444dcffffeVsazahFTZhj6mv","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_847852207b0945ccb53994bd","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-038/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-038/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-038: Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager) — Design\n2: \n3: ## 1. Architecture\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 Purpose\n6: \n7: This AR covers comprehensive Go unit tests for the `pkg/workloadmanager` module, including handler, middleware, reconciler, response sub-packages and top-level constants.\n8: \n9: ### 1.2 System Context\n10: \n11: ```\n12: pkg/workloadmanager/\n13: ├── const.go              # Constants/enums\n14: ├── const_test.go         # NEW — constant validation tests\n15: ├── handler/\n16: │   ├── *.go              # HTTP handlers\n17: │   └── *_test.go         # NEW — handler tests\n18: ├── middleware/\n19: │   ├── *.go              # HTTP middleware\n20: │   └── *_test.go         # NEW — middleware tests\n21: ├── reconciler/\n22: │   ├── *.go              # State reconciler\n23: │   └── *_test.go         # NEW — reconciler tests\n24: └── response/\n25:     ├── *.go              # Response utilities\n26:     └── *_test.go         # NEW — response tests\n27: ```\n28: \n29: ### 1.3 Design Principles\n30: \n31: - **Table-driven tests**: Go idiom for test data organization\n32: - **No production code changes**: Only `*_test.go` additions\n33: - **httptest for handlers**: `net/http/httptest` for HTTP handler testing\n34: - **Interface-based mocking**: Abstract external dependencies behind interfaces\n35: - **Black-box + white-box**: Mix of `package_test` and `package_internal_test` as needed\n36: \n37: ---\n38: \n39: ## 2. Test Strategy by Sub-Package\n40: \n41: ### 2.1 handler/\n42: \n43: | Test Category | Approach |\n44: |---------------|----------|\n45: | Request parsing | Valid/invalid JSON, missing fields, type mismatches |\n46: | Response construction | Status codes, body format, headers |\n47: | Error handling | 4xx/5xx scenarios, panic recovery |\n48: | Edge cases | Empty body, oversized payload, concurrent requests |\n49: \n50: ### 2.2 middleware/\n51: \n52: | Test Category | Approach |\n53: |---------------|----------|\n54: | Auth middleware | Valid token, expired token, missing token, malformed token |\n55: | Logging middleware | Output capture, request ID propagation |\n56: | Validation middleware | Pass-through, rejection with error response |\n57: | Recovery middleware | Panic caught, 500 returned, stack trace logged |\n58: \n59: ### 2.3 reconciler/\n60: \n61: | Test Category | Approach |\n62: |---------------|----------|\n63: | State sync | Current vs desired state convergence |\n64: | Retry logic | Max retries, backoff, success after retry |\n65: | Idempotency | Repeated calls produce same result |\n66: | Error propagation | Dependency failure handling |\n67: \n68: ### 2.4 response/\n69: \n70: | Test Category | Approach |\n71: |---------------|----------|\n72: | JSON serialization | Struct → JSON, nil fields, special characters |\n73: | Error code mapping | Internal error → HTTP status, custom codes |\n74: | Helper functions | Response writers, header setting |\n75: \n76: ### 2.5 const.go\n77: \n78: | Test Category | Approach |\n79: |---------------|----------|\n80: | Enum completeness | All expected values present |\n81: | Boundary conditions | Min/max values, zero values |\n82: | String representations | `String()` methods (if any) |\n83: \n84: ---\n85: \n86: ## 3. Testing Patterns\n87: \n88: ### 3.1 Table-Driven Test Template\n89: \n90: ```go\n91: func TestHandler_Foo(t *testing.T) {\n92:     tests := []struct {\n93:         name       string\n94:         input      RequestType\n95:         wantStatus int\n96:         wantBody   string\n97:         wantErr    bool\n98:     }{\n99:         {\n100:             name:       \"valid request\",\n101:             input:      RequestType{Field: \"value\"},\n102:             wantStatus: http.StatusOK,\n103:             wantBody:   `{\"status\":\"ok\"}`,\n104:             wantErr:    false,\n105:         },\n106:         {\n107:             name:       \"invalid request\",\n108:             input:      RequestType{},\n109:             wantStatus: http.StatusBadRequest,\n110:             wantBody:   `{\"error\":\"...\"}`,\n111:             wantErr:    true,\n112:         },\n113:     }\n114: \n115:     for _, tt := range tests {\n116:         t.Run(tt.name, func(t *testing.T) {\n117:             // Arrange\n118:             req := httptest.NewRequest(http.MethodPost, \"/path\", toJSON(tt.input))\n119:             w := httptest.NewRecorder()\n120: \n121:             // Act\n122:             handler(w, req)\n123: \n124:             // Assert\n125:             assert.Equal(t, tt.wantStatus, w.Code)\n126:             if tt.wantBody != \"\" {\n127:                 assert.JSONEq(t, tt.wantBody, w.Body.String())\n128:             }\n129:         })\n130:     }\n131: }\n132: ```\n133: \n134: ### 3.2 Mock Pattern\n135: \n136: ```go\n137: type mockDependency struct {\n138:     // Record calls\n139:     calls []string\n140:     // Configure behavior\n141:     err error\n142: }\n143: \n144: func (m *mockDependency) DoSomething() error {\n145:     m.calls = append(m.calls, \"DoSomething\")\n146:     return m.err\n147: }\n148: ```\n149: \n150: ---\n151: \n152: ## 4. Coverage Targets\n153: \n154: | Sub-Package | Target Coverage | Rationale |\n155: |-------------|-----------------|-----------|\n156: | handler/ | 80%+ | Core user-facing logic |\n157: | middleware/ | 85%+ | Critical path, many edge cases |\n158: | reconciler/ | 75%+ | Complex state machine |\n159: | response/ | 90%+ | Simple utilities, should be fully covered |\n160: | const.go | 100% | Trivial but important |\n161: \n162: ---\n163: \n164: ## 5. Implementation Notes\n165: \n166: - Use `go test -cover` to measure coverage\n167: - Run `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` to execute all tests\n168: - No external services required — all dependencies mocked\n169: - Tests should be deterministic (no flaky tests)\n\n(End of file - total 169 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-038: Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager) — Design\n\n## 1. Architecture\n\n### 1.1 Purpose\n\nThis AR covers comprehensive Go unit tests for the `pkg/workloadmanager` module, including handler, middleware, reconciler, response sub-packages and top-level constants.\n\n### 1.2 System Context\n\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/\n├── const.go              # Constants/enums\n├── const_test.go         # NEW — constant validation tests\n├── handler/\n│   ├── *.go              # HTTP handlers\n│   └── *_test.go         # NEW — handler tests\n├── middleware/\n│   ├── *.go              # HTTP middleware\n│   └── *_test.go         # NEW — middleware tests","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-038/design.md","time":{"start":1775897372295,"end":1775897372314}}}}
